name: The King's Dreams: A Colonial Mystery
description:
Armour. Metal and chains. The clangs were unfamiliar to the sounds of the wild. There was none who understood these noises but it was the arrival of a new age.
An age of change.
The men in the strange suits spoke loudly and saliva poured from their bearded mouths.
They were rattled and raucous.
A sign they were afraid of the unknown.
But the elders saw them coming.
They lit fires.
They poured ashes across the perimeter.
Ready but unprepared.
Alerted and highly conscious.
